WEBVTT

00:01.960 --> 00:03.450
(ROARING)

00:03.545 --> 00:07.037
NARRATOR: <i>He is the apex predator
of the Arctic.</i>

00:08.383 --> 00:11.500
<i>Now, the ice bear is under siege.</i>

00:12.554 --> 00:15.762
<i>The threat, an adversary that's deadlier,</i>

00:16.058 --> 00:19.221
<i>more powerful than any he 's ever faced.</i>

00:20.562 --> 00:21.768
(SQUAWKING)

00:21.855 --> 00:25.643
<i>A gauntlet of challenges
beyond any the Arctic has dealt him.</i>

00:28.403 --> 00:29.688
(BUZZING)

00:36.036 --> 00:37.276
(GROWLS)

00:37.371 --> 00:40.534
<i>After millions of years of ruling the ice,</i>

00:41.917 --> 00:45.000
<i>has the polar bear met his match?</i>

00:47.000 --> 00:53.074
